<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/navbar.css">
</head>
<body>
    {{>navbar}}
   <header class="about-hero">
        <div class="about-hero-overlay"></div>
        <div class="about-hero-content">
            <h1 class="about-hero-title">About Us</h1>
            <p class="about-hero-description">Learn more about our journey and values.</p>
            <a href="/" class="about-hero-link">Back to Home</a>
        </div>
    </header>



            <div class="about-content">
                <img src="/images/our-story.jpeg" alt="Our Story" class="about-image">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <p>Our journey began with a passion for unique, handmade goods. We believe in the beauty and value of artisanal craftsmanship, and our mission is to connect talented artisans with customers who appreciate the artistry and dedication that goes into each piece.</p>
                    <p>We started this marketplace to provide a platform where handmade goods can be celebrated and shared with the world. Every item in our collection is carefully curated to ensure the highest quality and uniqueness.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section values-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Our Values</h2>
            <div class="values-content">
                <div class="value-card">
                    <img src="/images/value-quality.jpeg" alt="Quality">
                    <h3>Quality</h3>
                    <p>We are committed to offering the highest quality handmade goods, crafted with care and precision.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <img src="/images/value-community.jpeg" alt="Community">
                    <h3>Community</h3>
                    <p>We support and empower artisans, helping them reach a wider audience and grow their businesses.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <img src="/images/sustainability.jpeg" alt="Sustainability">
                    <h3>Sustainability</h3>
                    <p>We promote sustainable practices, ensuring that our products are ethically made and environmentally friendly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section team-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Meet the Team</h2>
            <div class="team-grid">
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="/images/seema.jpeg" alt="Team Member 1">
                    <h3>Seema Sangwan</h3>
                    <p>Founder & CEO</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="/images/urvashi.jpeg" alt="Team Member 2">
                    <h3>urvashi</h3>
                    <p>Chief Marketing Officer</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="/images/seema2.jpeg" alt="Team Member 3">
                    <h3>Seema</h3>
                    <p>Lead Designer</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Handmade Goods Marketplace. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
